README

NEEDFULL:
LINUX, WITH FREE, UNBUSYED PORTS: 3000 (for nginx), 8000-8007 (for backends)

AUTO-INSTALL FOR DEBIAN / ARCHLINUX:
./mir-control setup


TO START BACKEND:
./mir-control www
./mir-control nginx
OR JUST:
./mir-control start


TO OPEN MIR IN BROWSER:
http://127.0.0.1:3000/


FRO AHOTHER OS OR FOR MANUAL READ NEXT:
##########################################################
HOW TO INSTALL MIR KERNEL ON DEBIAN / UBUNTU:

sudo apt install cpanminus make build-essential

cpanm AnyEvent
cpanm EV
cpanm AnyEvent::HTTPD

Thats all

Try to start: 
./scripts/mir

INSTALL nginx:
STEP BY STEP
cd nginx/nginx-1.22.0-src
./configure --prefix=../
make && make install && make clean
cd ../
cp nginx.conf conf/nginx.conf
cd ../

STARTING NGINX:
cd nginx/sbin && ./nginx && cd ../../



